---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Bet on Our Becoming · Quest Labs">

<div class="bet-page">

  <div class="bet-hero">
    <div class="bet-eyebrow"><span class="bet-ql">Quest Labs</span> 2026</div>
    <h1 class="bet-title">Bet on our<br>becoming.</h1>
    <p class="bet-sub">Wish you could do something to materially shift the trajectory of a wayward world driven by nefarious nonsense? You can. This is how.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="bet-body-section">
    <p class="bet-body">Quest Labs is fueled by <strong>FAITH</strong>, and by people who believe that real change starts in the body, the community, and the classroom long before it shows up in the news.</p>

    <div class="faith-block">
      <div class="faith-row"><span class="faith-letter">F</span><span class="faith-word">Finding</span></div>
      <div class="faith-row"><span class="faith-letter">A</span><span class="faith-word">Alternative</span></div>
      <div class="faith-row"><span class="faith-letter">I</span><span class="faith-word">Innovative</span></div>
      <div class="faith-row"><span class="faith-letter">T</span><span class="faith-word">Transformative</span></div>
      <div class="faith-row"><span class="faith-letter">H</span><span class="faith-word">Heartspaces</span></div>
      <p class="faith-sub">A coaching quest. A futures practice. A heart-led becoming.</p>
    </div>

    <p class="bet-body">You're not buying a product. This isn't charity. You're betting on a future we haven't seen and can't make sense of just yet... one we can feel calling... one our future ancestors are praying for.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="bet-tiers-section">
    <div class="bet-section-label">Choose your bet</div>

    <!-- Tier 1 -->
    <div class="bet-tier">
      <div class="bet-tier-top">
        <div>
          <div class="bet-tier-symbol">🔥</div>
          <h2 class="bet-tier-name">Spark</h2>
          <p class="bet-tier-tagline">One light. One life. One ripple.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bet-tier-price">$500</div>
      </div>
      <p class="bet-tier-desc">Fund one participant's place in a 12-week Quest Labs cohort. Name someone specific, or leave the seat open for whoever needs it most. A single spark is how every fire starts.</p>
      <a href="https://www.paypal.com/ncp/payment/6DCPDYTQT536A" class="bet-pay-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Bet $500 via PayPal →</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Tier 2 (featured) -->
    <div class="bet-tier bet-tier--featured">
      <div class="bet-tier-top">
        <div>
          <div class="bet-tier-symbol">👥</div>
          <h2 class="bet-tier-name">The Pair</h2>
          <p class="bet-tier-tagline">Because it takes two to tango.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bet-tier-price">$1,000</div>
      </div>
      <p class="bet-tier-desc">Two seats, fully flexible: same cohort or different, your call or theirs. Send them to anyone, anytime. No strings.</p>
      <a href="https://www.paypal.com/ncp/payment/ZLWJJH3EVH4MJ" class="bet-pay-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Bet $1,000 via PayPal →</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Tier 3 -->
    <div class="bet-tier">
      <div class="bet-tier-top">
        <div>
          <div class="bet-tier-symbol">💫</div>
          <h2 class="bet-tier-name">The Constellation</h2>
          <p class="bet-tier-tagline">A pattern emerges.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bet-tier-price">$5,000</div>
      </div>
      <p class="bet-tier-desc">Ten seats for a school, a team, a community you believe in. Enough to shift a staff room, a department, a cohort of educators. This is where institutional change starts: not in policy in boardrooms, but in communities of praxis.</p>
      <a href="https://www.paypal.com/ncp/payment/GR3WJPK28RWZ4" class="bet-pay-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Bet $5,000 via PayPal →</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Tier 4 -->
    <div class="bet-tier">
      <div class="bet-tier-top">
        <div>
          <div class="bet-tier-symbol">🪐</div>
          <h2 class="bet-tier-name">The Universe</h2>
          <p class="bet-tier-tagline">Water Earthseed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bet-tier-price">$10,000</div>
      </div>
      <p class="bet-tier-desc">Foundation-level partnership. You fund an entire cohort from the ground up, and you don't disappear when the check clears. This tier comes with real-time, collaborative documentation of the work as it unfolds: participant-voiced, Quest Labs-curated, the most wholesome social media feed we're thirsty for.</p>
      <ul class="bet-tier-perks">
        <li>Named cohort sponsorship</li>
        <li>Collaborative real-time updates from participants and the Quest Labs team</li>
        <li>Positive social documentation: living proof something extraordinary is happening</li>
        <li>Direct line to the Quest Labs founders throughout the cohort</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="https://www.paypal.com/ncp/payment/RAHEVMFETBX4U" class="bet-pay-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Bet $10,000 via PayPal →</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Tier 5 -->
    <div class="bet-tier">
      <div class="bet-tier-top">
        <div>
          <div class="bet-tier-symbol">🎁</div>
          <h2 class="bet-tier-name">The Wish</h2>
          <p class="bet-tier-tagline">As you wish.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bet-tier-price">Any amount</div>
      </div>
      <p class="bet-tier-desc">You know what feels right. Every contribution goes directly into keeping this work alive, accessible, and audacious. No amount is too small to matter.</p>
      <a href="https://www.paypal.com/ncp/payment/XKNZVQHFY7QYJ" class="bet-pay-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Make a wish via PayPal →</a>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="page-bridge" style="max-width:860px; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto; padding-left:2.5rem; padding-right:2.5rem;">
    <p class="bet-closing-cta">For larger partnerships, institutional funding, or conversations about embedding Quest Labs in your world:</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="bridge-link">Let's talk →</a>
  </div>

</div>

<footer>
  <div class="footer-inner">
    <div>
      <div class="footer-logo">Quest Labs</div>
      <div class="footer-tagline">Healing-Centered Futures</div>
    </div>
    <ul class="footer-links">
      <li><a href="/program">FLIP</a></li>
      <li><a href="/educators">Educators</a></li>
      <li><a href="/foundations">Foundations</a></li>
      <li><a href="/black-menagerie">Black Menagerie</a></li>
      <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="footer-copy">2026 Quest Labs · Makēda · All futures reserved · Berlin &amp; Beyond</div>
</footer>

</Layout>

<style>
  .bet-page { padding-top: 1rem; }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .bet-hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5rem 2rem 3rem;
  }
  .bet-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--teal);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: progFadeUp 0.8s ease 0.2s forwards;
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .bet-ql {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #ffffff;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .bet-title {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold-pale);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: progFadeUp 0.8s ease 0.4s forwards;
  }
  .bet-sub {
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: progFadeUp 0.8s ease 0.6s forwards;
  }

  /* ── BODY SECTION ── */
  .bet-body-section {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 3rem auto;
    padding: 0 2.5rem;
  }
  .bet-body {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .bet-body strong { color: var(--text); }

  /* ── FAITH BLOCK ── */
  .faith-block {
    border-left: 2px solid var(--violet);
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    background: rgba(107,63,160,0.06);
    border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
  }
  .faith-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .faith-letter {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--violet-light);
    min-width: 1.2rem;
  }
  .faith-word {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .faith-sub {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--teal);
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  /* ── TIERS ── */
  .bet-tiers-section {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 4rem auto;
    padding: 0 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }
  .bet-section-label {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--teal);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .bet-tier {
    background: rgba(107,63,160,0.05);
    border: 0.5px solid rgba(107,63,160,0.25);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .bet-tier:hover { border-color: rgba(180,143,224,0.4); }
  .bet-tier--featured {
    border-color: rgba(107,63,160,0.5);
    background: rgba(107,63,160,0.1);
  }
  .bet-tier-top {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .bet-tier-symbol {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--violet-light);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .bet-tier-name {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .bet-tier-tagline {
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
  }
  .bet-tier-price {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gold-pale);
    white-space: nowrap;
    padding-top: 0.25rem;
  }
  .bet-tier-desc {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .bet-tier-perks {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .bet-tier-perks li {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    padding-left: 1rem;
    border-left: 1.5px solid rgba(107,63,160,0.4);
  }
  .bet-pay-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text);
    background: var(--violet);
    padding: 0.8rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 2px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .bet-pay-btn:hover { background: var(--violet-mid, #8B5CC8); }

  /* ── CLOSING ── */
  .bet-closing-cta {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .bet-tier-top { flex-direction: column; }
    .bet-tiers-section { padding: 0 1.5rem; }
    .bet-body-section { padding: 0 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>
